
Mingw64 installation for Windows
-------------------------------

Download page: https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/

The package: x86_64-win32-seh

Download and unzip the files to the directory "C:\"



Setting Path environments:
--------------------------

Open the panel that is used in order to set path variables.

The panel can be opened with the way given in below.


Control Panel -> System and Security -> System -> Advanced System Settings ->Environment Variables


The following paths must be added to the user path ( The path variables to be used for the users )

mingw64

mingw64\bin

mingw64\include

mingw64\x86_64-w64-mingw32

mingw64\x86_64-w64-mingw32\include

mingw64\x86_64-w64-mingw32\lib
